      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OLD HABITS (2) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at this track over 400m behind Paw Ferna (23.20) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. TAKE THE EDGE (6) was quickly into stride and burnt early from the middle draw where she gave a sight, finishing second (23.20) and beaten 2.75 lengths over 400m at this track. Will give a great sight again. ALLIE (1) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 12 lengths back in third (24.49) at Bendigo in a Special conditions H over 425m. Can measure up. WARRIOR PAGE (4) scored last time and appeals as a top-three prospect.",
